children.value: This summer in addition to moving, working, and trying to enjoy some sunshine I have spent a number of evenings held up in my room trying to learn how to develop an app for the Android OS. It was actually a lot of fun, and I think I was able to walk away (not really, I’m still gonna work on it) with a pretty nifty app!
I encourage you to check it out if you have an Android device, and give me some feedback on what you think, what you like, what you think I could add! Happy movie searching!
